OL,3,CChancellor 'must raise taxes to help
OL,4,Cplug #40bn-plus gap to meet fiscal
OL,5,Crule'
OL,7,FThe Chancellor must resort to
OL,8,F"moderate but sustained" tax rises to
OL,9,Fhelp repair Britain's battered public
OL,10,Ffinances as she faces missing one of
OL,11,Fher fiscal rules by more than #40
OL,12,Fbillion, an economic think tank has
OL,13,Fwarned.
OL,15,FThe National Institute of Economic and
OL,16,FSocial Research (Niesr) said weaker-
OL,17,Fthan-expected recent economic
OL,18,Factivity, U-turns on welfare cuts and
OL,19,Fforecast-beating borrowing have
OL,20,Fcombined to create a "worsening fiscal
OL,21,Foutlook".
