OL,3,CChancellor 'must raise taxes to help
OL,4,Cplug #40bn-plus gap to meet fiscal
OL,5,Crule'
OL,7,FRachel Reeves is now set for a #41.2
OL,8,Fbillion shortfall on her "stability
OL,9,Frule" in 2029-30 and has been left
OL,10,Fwith an "impossible trilemma" of
OL,11,Ftrying to meet her fiscal rules while
OL,12,Ffulfilling spending commitments and
OL,13,Fupholding a manifesto pledge to not
OL,14,Fraise taxes, it said.
OL,16,FShe will need to raise taxes or cut
OL,17,Fspending in the autumn budget to plug
OL,18,Fthe gap, Niesr cautioned.
