OL,5,Crule'
OL,7,FThis comes despite Niesr nudging up
OL,8,Fits economic outlook for the UK, with
OL,9,Fgrowth of 1.3% now pencilled in for
OL,10,F2025, up from 1.2% forecast in May.
OL,12,FBut the group cut its prediction for
OL,13,Fnext year ` to 1.2%, down from 1.5%
OL,14,Fpreviously expected.
OL,16,FNiesr has urged the Government to look
OL,17,Fat addressing the public finance woes
OL,18,Fby building a "large fiscal buffer via
OL,19,Fa moderate but sustained increase in
OL,20,Ftaxes".
