OL,7,FThe Chancellor has set herself two
OL,8,Ffiscal rules ` the "stability rule",
OL,9,Fwhich ensures that day-to-day spending
OL,10,Fis matched by tax revenues so the
OL,11,FGovernment only borrows to invest, and
OL,12,Fthe "investment rule", which requires
OL,13,Fthe Government to reduce net financial
OL,14,Fdebt as a share of the economy.
