OL,7,FShadow chancellor Sir Mel Stride said:
OL,8,F"Experts are warning Labour's economic
OL,9,Fmismanagement has blown a black hole
OL,10,Fin the nation's finances which will
OL,11,Fhave to be filled with more tax rises
OL,12,F` despite Rachel Reeves saying she
OL,13,Fwouldn't be back for more taxes.
OL,15,F"Labour will always reach for the tax
OL,16,Frise lever because they don't
OL,17,Funderstand the economy."
